Full PTM Table Example

ex_full_ptm_table.Rd

Post-translational modification data under certain environmental conditions.

Usage

ex_full_ptm_table

Format

Dataframe of 497 rows and 72 columns:

row

Number of PTMs

columns

Names of drugs that were used on PTMs

values

Expression as found by mass spectrometry

Source

"An .rda version of phospho_cleaned_mapped.txt found in inst/extdata"
